    <abstract>
      <para>This is the main page of the MMBase documentation. All
      documentation should be listed here. It has several sections targeted at
      different groups of users and developers. More about the documentation
      structure can be read in the document <ulink
      url="documentation.pdf">About MMBase Documentation</ulink>.</para>
